                                                   "title":  "Complete Arrival Card / Digital Arrival Card",
                                                   "description":  "Thailand phased out the paper TM6 card at major airports in 2022. A Thailand Digital Arrival Card (TDAC) system is in use â€” check current requirements before travel. If issued a paper TM6 on the aircraft, fill in your passport details, Thai address, and flight number."
